Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.25,0:00:15.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子(れつこ)）空前の盛り上がりを見せた\N経理部の飲み会から 一夜 明け―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:15.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The drinking party for Accounting\Nlast night saw sparks fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:18.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, another day begins at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:19.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,今日も また\N会社での一日が始まります
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:23.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子(こ)）うえ～\N完全に 二日酔いだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:23.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I am completely hungover.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:28.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,飲み会の最後らへん\N全然 覚えてなくってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:28.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even remember\Nhow the party ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:31.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Didn't Retsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）確か 烈子が…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:36.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（延髄をたたく音）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:43.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure Retsuko\Nsang some sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:43.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田(だ)）確か 烈子は\Nカラオケで何か歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（たたく音）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:48.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）幸運なことに\N泥酔していた同僚たちは―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:51.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, my inebriated co-workers\Ndon't seem to clearly remember last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:51.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,その日の記憶が 全く ないようです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:53.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,残る問題は…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:53.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The only problem left...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:55.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（足音）\N（烈子）うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:00:58.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トンのうなり声）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:01.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お… おはようございます
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:01.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:03.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トンのうなり声）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:07.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry about last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:07.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あ… あの… き… 昨日は\Nいろいろと すみませんでした！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:10.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,酒の席とはいえ 数々のご無礼―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:12.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Drunkenness is not an excuse\Nfor being as rude as I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:12.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,申し開きのしようも\Nございません
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:17.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）覚えてねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:16.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:18.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:22.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,昨日は飲み過ぎちまってな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:22.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I drank way too much last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:24.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:24.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:28.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:27.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,RAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:05.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,KARAOKE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:09.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美(わしみ)）じゃあ 烈子の―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:12.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,So you managed to retain your reputation\Nas a responsible good girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,真面目な いい子のイメージは\N保たれたままってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:15.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）そうみたいですね\N（鷲美）何だ つまんない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:15.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-It seems so.\N-Well, that's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:17.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,もう ひと事だと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:17.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please! I much prefer it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:23.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あの ところで―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:26.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,さっきから ゴリ部長が 隣で\N石になって固まってるんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:27.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,why is Director Gori frozen like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:30.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）\Nああ いいのよ 気にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:31.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）めんどくさいことに\Nなるから ほっときなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:34.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not open that can of worms!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも 石になるなんて\Nよっぽどですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:36.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But she has turned into a statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何か あったんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:38.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:41.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）失恋したのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Heartbreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:50.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）でも まだ好きなの～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:54.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,確かに私も 仕事を言い訳に\Nしすぎちゃったとこは あるわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:54.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I was always\Nusing my job as an excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:58.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I also put up with a lot from him,\Nbut I was so forgiving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも 私だって\Nいろいろ我慢してたし―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:58.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いろいろ\N許してあげてきたじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それが いけなかったのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:01.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that is where I went wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:04.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make him think\NI would forgive anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:04.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何しても許されると\N思わせちゃったのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:08.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have known that\Nwe wouldn't understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:08.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お互い 分かり合えるなんて\N思っちゃうのが間違いなんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We live in two different worlds,\Nafter all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だって ２人とも\N違う世界を見てるんだもの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ドライヤーの音）\N（ゴリ）聞いてる？ 烈子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Are you listening, Retsuko?\N-Why did you follow me home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だから 何で 家まで\Nついてきちゃうんですか！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,今夜は １人で\N寝る気にならないのよ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:18.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to sleep on my own tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:21.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いいかげん帰ってくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:21.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go back to your place already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:25.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いいじゃない別に\N烈子の部屋 一度見てみたかったし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:25.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind, do you? Besides,\NI've always wanted to check out your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:29.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）あっ このＴシャツ借りるわね\N（烈子）ちょっと～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:29.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-I'm borrowing this T-shirt.\N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）ねえ ほんとに\N好きな人いないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:35.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Is there really nobody you like?\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:35.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:39.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-No nice suitors at work?\N-Nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:39.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）会社に いい人いないの？\N（烈子）いません！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:41.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,打っても響かない子ね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to spill the beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,なら 想像くらい\Nしてみてもいいんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's nice to dream about it. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:47.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,この町の どこかに―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:51.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Your soulmate could be\Nsomewhere in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:51.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子にとって\N運命の人がいるかもしれないって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:01.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根(つぼね)）もう 何これ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:04.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,れさすけ君 困るわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Resasuke, this is problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:08.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have I told you\Nthat we don't accept illegible receipts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:07.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,“読めない領収書なんか\N受け取れない”って いつも―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,言ってるわよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）すいません
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:14.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess. You put it\Nin your back pocket and forgot about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,また ズボンのポッケに\N入れっぱなしで 何日も―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ほったらかしにしてたんでしょう？\N（れさすけ）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:15.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根）忘れて そのまま洗濯？\N（れさすけ）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-And then you put it through the wash?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:22.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ハア… じゃあ 今回も自腹ね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:22.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's another expense\Nyou have to cover yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:25.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）出た 自腹王子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The Out-of-Pocket Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,自腹王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:30.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-The Out-of-Pocket Prince?\N-The spaced-out guy from Sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:30.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あの ぼーっとした営業の人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:33.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-He always gets in trouble.\N-I don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いつも あの調子で怒られてんの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）あんな人 いたっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's not exactly memorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:36.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）確かに\N印象に残らないタイプだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ぶつかる音）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（角田(つのだ)）あっ 烈子先輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:49.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Retsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:51.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ 角田さん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Tsunoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:54.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking me out to dinner\Nthe other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（角田）先日は ご飯\Nごちそうになっちゃって―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,すみませんでした！ あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello to you too, Ms. Fenneko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,フェネ子先輩も こんにちは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:58.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）ヘヘ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:00.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,で いきなりなんですけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:00.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is abrupt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Is there someone you like?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,先輩 今\N好きな人とか います？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:03.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,は？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,い… いないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ 合コン 参加しません？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you join our singles mixer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:15.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,合コン！？\Nえー いいよ私はそういうの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,A mixer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:15.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm not into that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you want a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも 彼氏欲しいですよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:20.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,行きましょうよ\N出会いのチャンスですよ～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:20.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You should come.\NThis is your chance to meet some guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 先輩 出てくださいよ～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:26.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,角田 烈子にその気がないんだから\Nやめたら？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:26.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunoda, Retsuko isn't interested.\NCut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何でですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:30.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Why?\N-Mixers are on the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,時代は\N出会いなんて求めてないの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:35.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,A study in Japan has shown that 75% of men
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:35.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ある調査によれば 日本の\N20代～30代の独身男性の75％―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,独身女性の65％に―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:39.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,and 65% of women\Nin their 20s and 30s have no partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,交際相手がいない\Nという結果が出てる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:42.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,つまり コスパの悪い恋愛に\N見切りをつけて―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, more and more people
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:45.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,are choosing the more economical option\Nof single life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:45.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,独り身を選ぶ人が増えてるの！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ フェネ子先輩も\N参加します？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:49.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-With that in mind, do you want to join?\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:49.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）はあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:52.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "With that in mind"?\NDid you hear what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:52.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何で“じゃあ”でつなげんの？\N私の話聞いてた？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,聞いてたけど\N意味分かんないです～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but I didn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ フェネ子先輩も\N“出る”って言ってるし―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:59.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Fenneko said that she's coming,\Nso you should come as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子先輩も来てくださいよ～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:01.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）出るって言ってないし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:07.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美･ゴリ）合コン！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:08.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,A mixer? Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いいんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:12.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも 正直\Nそういうの苦手なんですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:11.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not used to such activities...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:15.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Your soulmate might be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:15.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子にとって\N運命の人が来るかもしれないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,運命の人って…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,My soulmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:20.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't fall in love that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:20.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私 そんな\Nほれっぽいタイプじゃないですし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）烈子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:29.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko, stop doubting yourself\Nand put yourself out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:30.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ごちゃごちゃ言ってないで\Nステージに上がるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,In the right circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:33.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）条件さえそろえば…\N（鷲美）恋に落ちるときは…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,...anyone can fall in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:34.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,...instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:34.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美･ゴリ）一瞬よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ハア～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:44.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）なっんで お前まで\Nぬるっと合コンに参加してんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:44.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you give into\Nthis mixer thing so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:46.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）私が聞きたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:46.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,正直 見くびってた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:48.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,角田があそこまで\N相手を―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:52.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize Tsunoda was so good\Nat dragging people into her schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,自分のペースに巻き込む\N技にたけてるとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（２人）ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも安心して… 私 守るから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-But don't worry. I'll protect her.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:02.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,血に飢えた\N男どもの攻撃から―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:04.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to protect Retsuko\Nfrom those bloodthirsty guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子を全力で守るから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,刺客として参戦するってことか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:06.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll go as her bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,頼むわ フェネ子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:11.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Fenneko!\NYou are my only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:11.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お前しか頼りになるやつ\Nいねえからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,任しといて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:13.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:32.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子のうめき声）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:36.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The Out-of-Pocket Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,自腹王子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:43.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,同じ電車 使ってたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,He travels on the same train.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,今まで全然 気付かなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,一応 降りたときに\N軽く挨拶くらい―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:51.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should say hi\Nwhen we get off the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:51.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,しといたほうがいいのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:52.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いやいや
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:55.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how would that\Namount to anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,下手に挨拶して\Nその後 どうするの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,話題もないし\N微妙な距離感で―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd end up quietly walking to work,\Nbut not quite together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,会社まで\N行くことになんない？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,っていうか そもそも―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:02.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he doesn't even know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,向こうは こっちのこと\N知らないかもだし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:04.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あ～ 超めんどくさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:06.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.\NI wish I hadn't noticed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,気付かなきゃ よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:19.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:23.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）えっ えっ 会社…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait… The office...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,超 変な人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:38.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two escape routes:\Nthe main entrance and the emergency exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:36.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）脱出経路は２つ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:38.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,正面入り口と 裏の非常口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:41.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get in trouble,\Nthe police station is opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何かあったら\Nはす向かいの交番に―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,駆け込むこと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）分かった？\N（烈子）う… うん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Got it?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:47.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,フェネ子先輩\Nもっと肩の力抜いてくださいよ～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Fenneko, please, just chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私 今日遊びで来てないし！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not here to relax, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:53.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子 変な男が狙ってきたら\N私が守るからね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:52.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko, I'll protect you\Nif some freak sets his sights on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,変な人なんて\N来るわけないじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:56.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No freaks are coming tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何で そう言い切れんのよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:02.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だって 来るの\Nうちの営業の人たちですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:02.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Because all of them\Nare from the Sales department.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:05.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）うちの営業？\N（角田）そうですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:05.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-From the office?\N-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,社内合コンって\N言ってませんでしたっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I mention it was a company mixer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（シャッター音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:13.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Company...\N-Mixer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:13.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）社内…\N（フェネ子）合コン
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:17.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Hi, I'm Manumaru!\N-Hello. I'm Rinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:16.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（マヌ丸(まる)）どうも マヌ丸っす
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（りんた）\Nはじめまして りんたです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら 挨拶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Say hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The Out-of-Pocket Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（２人）自腹王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（角田）えっ？\N（フェネ子･烈子）何でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-What?\N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ こいつは\Nれさすけっていいます
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy here is Resasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:36.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,人数合わせで連れてきたやつなんで\N飾りだと思ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:36.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,He came to even out the numbers,\Nso don't mind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,その言い方 ひどくないですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:39.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think\Nthat's a mean thing to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:42.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（マヌ丸･りんた）アハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:45.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,け… 経理部の烈子と申します
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:45.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Retsuko from Accounting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:50.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Nice to meet you. You're cute!\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:49.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,よろしく！\N烈子ちゃん かわいいっすねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えー…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You remind me of someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:53.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,誰かに似てんなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:53.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:56.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anyone ever said\Nyou resemble a Sanrio character?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:56.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,サンリオキャラに似てるって\N言われない？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ わりと言われる…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:58.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,On occasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:02.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子のうなり声）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:05.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（マヌ丸）角田 この子 誰？\N（角田）経理部のフェネ子先輩です
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:05.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Who is this, Tsunoda?\N-Fenneko, from Accounting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はじめまして！\Nフェネ子ちゃんも―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:09.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. You're cute, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:08.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,かわいいっすねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:12.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（エコー）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:14.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Mixers aren't that bad after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:15.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）合コン 悪くないかも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:18.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（マヌ丸たちの笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:20.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（マヌ丸）俺そういうの\N全然余裕だから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:21.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Oh, that's easy-peasy!\N-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:21.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（角田）それ\N本気で言ってます？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:24.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-To put it another way...\N-Where did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（りんた）それって\N言い方 変えるとさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）\Nそれ どこ情報？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（４人の笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:27.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（マヌ丸）いや マジ マジ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:29.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）だから…\N（りんた）いや ほんとかよ～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:32.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed my chance\Nto join the conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:32.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）すっかり\N会話から あぶれてしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ いいんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,not that I really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:41.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも つまらなそうにしてるのも\Nあれだしな…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:41.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to look bored, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えーと 話題 話題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What can we talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:49.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あの… 昨日\N電車で お見かけしましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:48.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, I saw you on the train yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いつも 田園都市線\N使ってるんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always use the Den-en-toshi line?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:56.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't get off at the station\Nclosest to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:56.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,会社の駅で降りずに\N行っちゃいましたよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:58.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:58.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれから どうしたんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっとですね…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:08.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:07.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お前\Nマジで ふざけんなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:08.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お前\Nマジで ふざけんなよ\N（角田たちの笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（りんた）アハハ…\N（フェネ子）ヘヘヘ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（りんた）いや お前\N面白いじゃないか なかなか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）えっ 今 何か言った？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:14.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:16.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子たちの笑い声）\N（りんた）何が出るかな 何が…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:19.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（マヌ丸たちの笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:21.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）声 ちっさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:21.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,He is so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,え？ すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It's a little noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっと うるさくて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:30.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子たちの話し声）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:36.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（操作音）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:43.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,ADD FRIEND
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,RESASUKE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:45.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,ADD
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:53.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（操作音）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:53.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,CONCERNING THE TRAIN...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I ARRIVED LATE.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:59.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,SEND
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:07.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning the train, I was daydreaming.\NI missed my stop and arrived late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,アハッ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:17.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:20.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you drinking coffee in a can?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not fond of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:26.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）ウフフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:29.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だからって\N普通 缶コーヒー 飲まないでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, but why coffee in a can?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）ハイ田 ねえ ハイ田！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:39.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Haida! Hey, Haida!\N-Don't shout. I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）\Nうるせえな！ 聞こえてるって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:43.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何かねえ 合コン\N思ってたより 超楽しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:43.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Mixers are a lot more fun than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）\Nんなこと どうでもいいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:48.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-How is Retsuko?\N-She's fine. No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子は どうなった？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）全然心配ない！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't cut out for this scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,やっぱ　あの子\Nこういうの向いてないね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何か ずっと下向いて\N携帯いじってるし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:54.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She spent the entire party\Ntapping away at her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）そっか…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:55.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）っていうか ハイ田\N情けねえんだよ お前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:13:01.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Haida, you're a wimp.\NGo and ask her out already, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:01.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,さっさと告っちまえ バーカ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:05.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cut out for partying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）ウフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I feel really relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:15.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何だか すごく落ち着いた気分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:20.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,まるで 私たちの周りだけ\N何も風が吹いてないみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:20.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a certain stillness\Nenveloping us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,COFFEE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:27.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:33.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私 酔ってんのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be getting drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,先輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:41.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子ちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（倒れる音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）烈子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:47.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Retsuko!\N-Retsuko, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:44.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（りんた）おい おいおい\Nえっ 大丈夫かよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（角田）烈子先輩\N大丈夫ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（りんた）おい おいおい\Nえっ 大丈夫かよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっと 烈子ちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:52.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）おかしいなあ\Nいつの間に こんな飲んだんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:52.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange...\NWhen did I manage to drink so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:02.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,RESTROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:08.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（デス烈子の吐く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）うう…\N（水洗音）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:16.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あ… ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:23.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）条件さえ そろえば…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:29.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,In the right circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）恋に落ちるときは…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:32.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,...anyone can fall in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,...instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美･ゴリ）一瞬よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:46.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:10.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,～♪
